com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Interface LucentV11Provider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CallCenterProvider, ITsapiProvider, ITsapiProviderEx, com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.ITsapiProviderEx2, LucentProvider, LucentV5Provider, LucentV7Provider, Provider

    public interface LucentV11Provider
extends LucentV7Provider
    This interface extends the Provider interface with Avaya-specific features. When a Provider is bound to a Avaya Communication Manager switch with PBX Driver Version 11 private data, this interface may be used to access additional capabilities. LucentV11Provider provides methods to check if the provider supports the endpoint registration events feature.
